{"tid":934624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孟晚舟用3本特區護照共33次遊走美加！香港政府或被認定為支那白手套而被取消《香港關係法》","createTime":"2018-12-09T11:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T06:37:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"014c46f813b259f81f7f36f7e309b41e129ca4ae","tid":934624,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181209/large/1544345298_10ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181209%2Flarge%2F1544345298_10ef.jpg&h=1c90d84e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為副董事長兼財務總監孟晚舟的保釋申請聆訊，將於溫哥華時間12月10日早上在加拿大卑詩省高級法院開庭續審。《蘋果》記者查閱美國海關及邊境保衞局的旅遊出入境紀錄，發現美國所指孟晚舟所持4本中國護照及3本香港特區護照中，孟只用香港特區護照申請美國旅遊簽證出入美國和加拿大。<br />\n<br />\n記者發現，根據法庭文件指出，孟晚舟持第二本特區護照（KJ040XXX2）從香港過境加拿大溫哥華，前往墨西哥，目前該護照被加國法庭扣留作為證物。港大法律學院首席講師張達明昨日在社交網站指，從美國司法部文件得悉，孟是用第二本護照（KJ040XXX2）入境加拿大，而並非用最新簽發的第三本護照（KJ047XXX8），這表示她在未註銷第二本護照情況下，獲簽發第三本護照。<br />\n<br />\n而美國海關及邊境保衞局的旅遊出入境紀錄顯示，孟晚舟的3本特區護照KJ020XXX3、KJ040XXX2、KJ047XXX8，均同樣顯示於2014年6月14日至2017年3月2日間、共33次美國出入境紀錄，紀錄完全一樣，而主要停留地點為紐約、波士頓、洛杉磯、西雅圖、佛羅里達州卡納維拉爾港（PCF Port Canaveral, FL）及溫哥華，而法庭文件則指，孟與前夫所生的16歲兒子目前正在波士頓求學，現任丈夫和10歲女兒則居住於溫哥華，而她自2017年3月2日開始，就避開前赴美國，但紀錄沒有顯示她在哪裏離境，而當時華為正接受美國當局調查。<br />\n<br />\n令人感到疑惑的是，為何孟晚舟3本特區護照的美國出入境紀錄完全一樣？究竟是在第2本護照未向香港入境處註銷情況下，申請第3本護照？還是美國簽證仍在第2本護照上，她需要拿取第2本和第3本護照一併出入境美國？正如張達明所言：「我仍然認為香港政府需要盡快徹查事件及作出公開解釋」。"},{"pid":"7d25ed2cd3b96950166ea229b0e00f5fc498a59f","tid":934624,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"source? 唔好燈please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ddb245844b2dabedfccdc7d6b5af8f9ad5d1a9","tid":934624,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港政府或會被TRUMP認定, <br />\n利用美國《香港關係法》區別對待身份, <br />\n協助支那進行損害美國利益既間諜活動<br />\n極良好理由, 國會取消《香港關係法》<br />\n堵塞間諜活動入口<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"db9b3f543bfa09088b5c6a3a3684c4d6cc595c55","tid":934624,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d25ed2cd3b96950166ea229b0e00f5fc498a59f","tid":934624,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"source? 唔好燈please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181209/59009795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59009795&d=7fkL%2F4v0HwSipFucVm8QWZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=60f5d2db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59009795&h=95ebf856\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181209/59009795</a>"},{"pid":"e11db5bf70224c1a485523a36599c86fe8ba269c","tid":934624,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db9b3f543bfa09088b5c6a3a3684c4d6cc595c55","tid":934624,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d25ed2cd3b96950166ea229b0e00f5fc498a59f","tid":934624,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"source? 唔好燈please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181209/59009795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59009795&d=7fkL%2F4v0HwSipFucVm8QWZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=60f5d2db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59009795&h=95ebf856\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/articl